import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { Trash2, Plus, Minus } from 'lucide-react'; import placeholder from '../assets/placeholder.svg'; const cartItems = [ { id: 1, name: 'Traditional A2 Cow Ghee', price: 29.99, quantity: 2, image: placeholder }, { id: 2, name: 'Organic Honey', price: 15.99, quantity: 1, image: placeholder }, ]; export default function Cart() { const total = cartItems.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.price * item.quantity, 0); return (

Your Cart

{cartItems.length === 0 ? (

Your cart is empty.

) : (
{cartItems.map((item) => (

{item.name}

${item.price.toFixed(2)}

{item.quantity}
))}

Order Summary

Subtotal ${total.toFixed(2)}
Shipping $5.00
Total ${(total + 5).toFixed(2)}
)}
); }
